short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: 在新标签页显示时间和收入信息

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension helps users quickly view the current week, the remaining days in the month, and the remaining days in the year, as well as track today’s earnings.
Users can customize various settings through the configuration page to meet their personal needs.
Suitable for users who need time management and income tracking.
